{"tid":442901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺有啲香港人真係自撚私到震","createTime":"2017-10-21T06:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T07:32:47.000Z","uid":84415,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77ff07bf946d066029805570f94d442994c934b0","tid":442901,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T06:17:30.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩一粥麵食晏喇，咁正常呢段就好撚多人既，咁我隔離檯就係一個師奶黎既，佢就一個人霸左張4人檯，食過一粥麵既都知道佢係快餐黎，咁個師奶一直都冇叫野食霸左半個鐘直至佢兩個仔黎，中間有幾個人問佢有冇人都話有人，咁撚多人既情況下佢都竟然可以咁厚顏無恥霸撚左半個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果個個都咁霸 間野執撚得了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：收皮喇自私撚，霸到夜晚呀笨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：收皮喇樓主，關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"6bd9324fa8fdfd571959655fceb83ff67c0ab96e","tid":442901,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T06:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5263aef34a71da7198e9e94c5f5719254f6c3943","tid":442901,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇打算同條女一齊都破佢處 自私到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌閪唔預我好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}